            <ns0:div type="translation" xml:lang="en" resp="#JP">
                <ns0:p>Agathe, a Christian, died in the month of May, 14 (days) from the kalends, 17 (days) remaining (to the end of the month)</ns0:p>
            </ns0:div>
            <ns0:div type="commentary">
                <ns0:p>The dating formula is unusual, but is attested in the Rabat catacomb in Malta (so Rizzone).</ns0:p>
                    
